      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Honest poor-condition car best suited for a buyer looking for a project, parts car, or basic transportation with work needed. Expect noticeable cosmetic wear inside and out, including visible paint flaws, dents, scuffs, and a tired interior with age and use showing throughout. It\u2019s not a clean turnkey vehicle, and a buyer should plan on maintenance and repairs to bring it up to a more dependable standard. If you want something inexpensive and understand what a rough car entails, this could be a workable option.",
