      "description": "$33,500 - Well-kept, clean, and ready to enjoy, this good-condition car presents nicely inside and out and has clearly been cared for. It shows the light, normal wear you\u2019d expect from a used vehicle, but overall it\u2019s a solid, attractive car that should make a great buy for someone wanting quality without paying top-tier money.",
