      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle is a practical option for someone seeking basic transportation, a project car, or a parts donor. It offers strong value for the money and an opportunity for the right buyer to put it to work. A straightforward, affordable choice with plenty of potential.",
