    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t fancy, and I want to be upfront that it shows its age, but it still has the kind of solid, honest character that makes it a great budget-friendly runaround, project, or spare vehicle. If you\u2019re after something affordable and approachable rather than perfect, this could be a really smart buy.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with strong enthusiast potential and a surprisingly eager drivetrain. The engine starts up with good character, the transmission engages, and the chassis feels like a worthwhile platform for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present, but the fundamentals make this a great budget entry for a builder, parts donor, or weekend revival. If you want an affordable car with mechanical promise and room to add value, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
